message.text:
𝐖𝐞𝐥𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐨 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐋𝐢𝐦𝐢𝐭𝐥𝐞𝐬𝐬 𝐒𝐤𝐢𝐞𝐬 𝐨𝐟 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐂𝐨𝐥𝐥𝐞𝐠𝐞 𝐘 𝐂𝐥𝐮𝐛! 🧡🍃♾️

We are beyond excited to welcome our new Y’ers on board as we rise together toward greater leadership, creativity, and impact on our campus community.🌟

Your journey begins here! Filled with opportunities to grow through leadership programs, advocacy projects, and events. 

This is your chance to showcase your talents, share your passions, and build meaningful friendships with fellow Y’ers who will make this year truly unforgettable.

Together, let’s make this academic year not only memorable but also inspiring and impactful for everyone. Here’s to flying higher and brighter with CYC!🎈🌟

#CYCibolSaHimPAMPawid
#DefyingLimits
#TheLegaCYContinues
#CYC27
#TamHunt2025 

Caption by Alexine Medenilla
Publication Material by Angela Courtney Reynoso

𝐖𝐞𝐥𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐨 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐋𝐢𝐦𝐢𝐭𝐥𝐞𝐬𝐬 𝐒𝐤𝐢𝐞𝐬 𝐨𝐟 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐄𝐔 𝐂𝐨𝐥𝐥𝐞𝐠𝐞 𝐘 𝐂𝐥𝐮𝐛! 🧡🍃♾️

We are beyond excited to welcome our new Y’ers on board as we rise together toward greater leadership, creativity, and impact on our campus community.🌟

Your journey begins here! Filled with opportunities to grow through leadership programs, advocacy projects, and events. 

This is your chance to showcase your talents, share your passions, and build meaningful friendships with fellow Y’ers who will make this year truly unforgettable.

Together, let’s make this academic year not only memorable but also inspiring and impactful for everyone. Here’s to flying higher and brighter with CYC!🎈🌟

#CYCibolSaHimPAMPawid
#DefyingLimits
#TheLegaCYContinues
#CYC27
#TamHunt2025
